### Risk-Guard API 整合測試 (IDEA HTTP Client)
# 
# 使用說明:
# 1. 直接點擊請求旁的綠色執行按鈕
# 2. 執行「Login」後，accessToken 會自動被儲存在全域變數中
# 3. 後續請求會自動帶入該 Token

@api_base = http://localhost:8080/api
@email = test@example.com
@password = Test123!

### [1] 登入 (Login)
# 獲取 accessToken 並寫入全域變數
# @no-cookie-jar
POST {{api_base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
    client.test("Request executed successfully", function() {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "Response status is not 200");
    });

    if (response.body.data && response.body.data.accessToken) {
        client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.data.accessToken);
        client.log("AccessToken captured: " + client.global.get("auth_token").substring(0, 10) + "...");
    }
%}

### [2] 獲取選單 (Get Menu)
# 需要 Bearer Token
GET {{api_base}}/menu
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Accept: application/json

### [3] 獲取個人資料 (Get Me)
# 驗證使用者身份與權限
GET {{api_base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Accept: application/json


### [4] 刷新 Access Token (Refresh)
# 使用 Cookie 中的 refresh_token (如果有的話)
#@no-cookie-jar
POST {{api_base}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

### [5] 登出 (Logout)
# 清除後端會話並作廢 Token
POST {{api_base}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
